http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/They-say-it-with-toffees/article13999169.ece

Those observing traffic rules while driving their vehicles were in for a surprise. As part of a traffic awareness programme, Visakha Container Terminal Pvt. Ltd in association with the City Police organised the programme at Tycoon and Lepakshi junctions on Wednesday and distributed chocolates to those following traffic rules.The week is observed from January 11 to 17. Employees of VCTPL and City Police took part in the campaign explaining people on the importance of road safety measures to be followed by pedestrians, two-wheeler and four-wheeler drivers, usage of pedestrian paths, Zebra crossing, wearing helmets, seat belts while driving and speed regulations.